    <p>
      So as we learned when performing the Grand Retribution Thrust, you will jump back before
      jumping forward with a thrust. Now there's a really cool tech where you can combine these two
      movements into the same direction, allowing you to close larger gaps and dealing massive
      damage in the process.
    </p>

